Signed, but not ratified:

* [[Law of the Sea]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://treaties.un.org/Pages/ViewDetailsIII.aspx?src=TREATY&mtdsg_no=XXI-6&chapter=21&Temp=mtdsg3&lang=en | title= LAW OF THE SEA 6 . United Nations Convention on the Law of the Sea Montego Bay, 10 December 1982  |website= United Nations  |date= December 10, 1982 |accessdate=May 26, 2015}}</ref>

