{{Expand French|Philippe Pinchemel|date=April 2012}}
'''Philippe Pinchemel''' (10 June 1923 – 16 March 2008) was a [[France|French]] geographer. He received the [[Lauréat Prix International de Géographie Vautrin Lud]] in 2004.

